</ul></nav></section><section class="front-matter"><div class="ameta p font-secondary font-xs">
<hgroup><h1>Effect of albumin fusion on the biodistribution of interleukin-2</h1></hgroup><div class="cg p">
<a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Yao%20Z"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id1"><span class="name western">Zhengsheng Yao</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id1">
<h3><span class="name western">Zhengsheng Yao</span></h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>1</sup>Human Genome Sciences, 14200 Shady Grove Road, Rockville, MD 20850 USA </div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Yao%20Z"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Zhengsheng Yao</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>1</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Dai%20W"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id2"><span class="name western">Weili Dai</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id2">
<h3><span class="name western">Weili Dai</span></h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>1</sup>Human Genome Sciences, 14200 Shady Grove Road, Rockville, MD 20850 USA </div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Dai%20W"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Weili Dai</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>1</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Perry%20J"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id3"><span class="name western">James Perry</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id3">
<h3><span class="name western">James Perry</span></h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>1</sup>Human Genome Sciences, 14200 Shady Grove Road, Rockville, MD 20850 USA </div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Perry%20J"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">James Perry</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>1</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Brechbiel%20MW"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id4"><span class="name western">Martin W Brechbiel</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id4">
<h3><span class="name western">Martin W Brechbiel</span></h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>2</sup>Department of Radiation Oncology, National Cancer Institute, Bethesda, MD 20892 USA </div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Brechbiel%20MW"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Martin W Brechbiel</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>2</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Sung%20C"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id5"><span class="name western">Cynthia Sung</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id5">
<h3><span class="name western">Cynthia Sung</span></h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>1</sup>Human Genome Sciences, 14200 Shady Grove Road, Rockville, MD 20850 USA </div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Sung%20C"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Cynthia Sung</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>1,</sup><sup>✉</sup>
</div>
<ul class="d-buttons inline-list">
<li><button class="d-button" aria-controls="aip_a" aria-expanded="false">Author information</button></li>
<li><button class="d-button" aria-controls="anp_a" aria-expanded="false">Article notes</button></li>
